    "This allows the identification of discussions related to a particular CT for further classification or network analysis.",
    "NLP techniques for analyzing CT contentIn exploring the realm of CTs and their narratives, several studies have employed NLP, computational analysis, and machine learning techniques to gain deeper insights.",
